    "Name": "Shogun",
    "Details": "The 4W is a custom variant of the Shogun brought by the Wolf's Dragoons to the Inner Sphere prior to the Clan Invasion. The fact it uses far more advanced technology than was available to the Great Houses meant its more efficient weapons loadout of two LRM-15 and four Streak SRM-6, combined with an ER PPC, really stood out.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Barrel Fist</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.21</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Lower, Right Lower</color>",
